         <div type="translation">
            <ab>In the 8th and 7th year, on Epeiph 25, has paid Chairemon son of Ptollas grandson of Arabikos, through Palemon . . ., forty-two drachmai, = 42 drachmai only. Artemidoros . . .</ab>
